On Mac OS X
===========

  $ brew install autoconf
  $ brew install popt
  $ autoheader
  $ autoconf
  $ touch ./config.h && ./configure
  $ make
  $ sudo make install

On GNU/Linux
============

  $ yum -y install popt-devel
  $ autoheader
  $ autoconf
  $ touch ./config.h && ./configure
  $ sudo make install

On AIX
============

  $ rpm -Uvh popt*.ppc.rpm
  $ autoheader
  $ autoconf
  $ touch ./config.h && ./configure
  $ sudo gmake install
